      },
      {
        "date": "247 years ago",
        "event": "Became archmage and Court Wizard"
      },
      {
        "date": "150 years ago",
        "event": "Sealed the Rift of Shadows, preventing demon invasion"
      },
      {
        "date": "50 years ago",
        "event": "Founded the Academy of High Magic"
      }
    ],
    "notes": "Elara is haunted by the memory of losing her mentor to dark magic. This drives her dedication to preventing others from falling to corruption."
